name: Framed Landscape #2
description:
This is part 2 of the Framed Landscape series.  

Glaciers are absolutely incredible beautiful formed over millennia.  Where the ice meets the water is so mesmerizing with all the shades of blue.  Unfortunately, the glaciers are melting too fast due to global warming, which is why I chose Tezos over a proof of work protocol for minting NFTs.  We should all take steps to combat global warming.
